OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fevening sunny spells as winds ease. A
OL,7,Fclear and cold night, with light winds
OL,8,Fand frost patches. Cloud increasing
OL,9,Ffrom the north late in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FCloudy, with rain through the
OL,12,Fmorning, then largely dry and bright
OL,13,Fwith sunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,14,Fshowers later. Breezy, though strong
OL,15,Fwinds near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
